# AXIS / CORPUS POSITION
#   Direct dependency on `kafkajs ^2.2.4` declared in package
#   .json — `kafkajs` is THE canonical pure-JavaScript Apache
#   Kafka client maintained by Tulios and contributors at the
#   tulios/kafkajs repository (3,800+ stars; the predominant
#   pure-JS Kafka client for Node.js — used by 514-labs/
#   moosestack, AnWeber/httpyac, codeedu/imersao-fullstack-
#   fullcycle, ever-q-server, jamesnixon197/kproto, kanli8/
#   iot_nodejs, NestDevLab/nestjs-yalc, oslabs-beta/xkite-cli,
#   ovotech/castle, RMLio/social-media-archiving, solzimer/
#   nsyslog, SouthwestAir/kleg, hoangsonww/Budget-Management-
#   Backend-API, madajaju/ailtire, and dozens of other
#   production Node.js applications.  kafkajs is *not*
#   librdkafka-based — it's a from-scratch native JS
#   implementation of the Kafka wire protocol, making it the
#   complement to `node-rdkafka` /  `@confluentinc/kafka-
#   javascript` for environments where you'd rather not link
#   against `librdkafka.so`).  kafkajs exposes the typed
